race.description: Valley Protective Services Max 150 Points Final F
race.comment: BUGATTI QUEEN (1) crossed over from out wide but caught the leaders turning before drawing clear to score (20.30) at this track in a Grade 5 over 350m. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Can make it back-to-back wins. GREAT MARLOW (2) was quickly into stride and burnt early from the middle draw where he gave a sight, finishing second (20.44) and beaten 2 lengths over 350m at this track. Winning chance. EVEN ME (8) has shown good improvement at his last two starts, most recently finishing 2nd at this track over 350m. Can measure up. WHAT'S THE PRICE (7) is among the chances again if she runs up to the latest effort.
